ATTENDANCE.GR_NO, CLASS_ALLOTMENT.ROLL_NO, concat(CLASS_ALLOTMENT.LAST_NAME,' ',CLASS_ALLOTMENT.FIRST_NAME,' ',CLASS_ALLOTMENT.FATHER_NAME) AS NAME, count(ATTENDACE_STATUS) AS HOLIDAYS  FROM NESPRESCHOOL.ATTENDANCE LEFT JOIN NESPRESCHOOL.CLASS_ALLOTMENT ON ATTENDANCE.GR_NO=CLASS_ALLOTMENT.GR_NO where ATTENDACE_STATUS='H' and attendance.GR_NO = '0014965' and  CLASS_ALLOTMENT.PRESENT_STD='JR KG' and CLASS_ALLOTMENT.PRESENT_DIV = 'BLUE' and ATTENDANCE.ACADEMIC_YEAR='2022-23' AND ATTENDACE_DATE BETWEEN '2022/06/01' AND '2023/05/31'  UNION ALL  (SELECT TOTAL_DAYS  FROM NESPRESCHOOL.ATTENDANCE LEFT JOIN NESPRESCHOOL.CLASS_ALLOTMENT ON ATTENDANCE.GR_NO=CLASS_ALLOTMENT.GR_NO where attendance.GR_NO = '0014965' and CLASS_ALLOTMENT.PRESENT_STD='JR KG' and ATTENDANCE.GR_NO, CLASS_ALLOTMENT.ROLL_NO, concat(CLASS_ALLOTMENT.LAST_NAME,' ',CLASS_ALLOTMENT.FIRST_NAME,' ',CLASS_ALLOTMENT.FATHER_NAME) AS NAME, count(ATTENDACE_STATUS) AS HOLIDAYS  FROM NESPRESCHOOL.ATTENDANCE LEFT JOIN NESPRESCHOOL.CLASS_ALLOTMENT ON ATTENDANCE.GR_NO=CLASS_ALLOTMENT.GR_NO where ATTENDACE_STATUS='H' and attendance.GR_NO = '0014935' and  CLASS_ALLOTMENT.PRESENT_STD='JR KG' and CLASS_ALLOTMENT.PRESENT_DIV = 'BLUE' and ATTENDANCE.ACADEMIC_YEAR='2022-23' AND ATTENDACE_DATE BETWEEN '2022/06/01' AND '2023/05/31'  UNION ALL  (SELECT TOTAL_DAYS  FROM NESPRESCHOOL.ATTENDANCE LEFT JOIN NESPRESCHOOL.CLASS_ALLOTMENT ON ATTENDANCE.GR_NO=CLASS_ALLOTMENT.GR_NO where attendance.GR_NO = '0014935' and CLASS_ALLOTMENT.PRESENT_STD='JR KG' and
